abstract_str: bahrain 's prince nasser bin hamad __al-khalifa__ let slip he is visiting london . the fourth son of the king , he is accused of torture in his home country . this week he posted a video of himself running in hyde park on instagram . campaigners have now handed over a ` dossier ' of new evidence to police . they are acting on behalf of a bahrain refugee identified only as __ff__ . prince nasser and the bahrain government strongly deny the accusations .
